

if whiteNoteName display = none and bg = white,
    bg color orange and whitenotename  show and color white.

else if whiteNoteName display show and bg color orange
    bg color blue

else if white note name display show and bg color blue
    bg color white and color black

else if white note name color black
    white note name display: hide



RANGE EXTENDER MODULE

Trim or extend in chunks of C-E or F-B so we always keep a white key on the end.

Store those two chunks as template literals.

extend treble : 
    if last child is b, add C-E chunk
    if last child is e, add F-b chunk

trim treble :
remove last child

trim bass :
remove first child